blog.name: friendsafariserver
blog.title: Friend Safari!
blog.description:
Friend Safari is a SFW, OC-friendly, paragraph-style roleplay server for main series Pokémon games. From Kanto to Alola, the whole Pokémon world is your Cloyster! Members of this server are allowed a total of four played characters, with at least one required to be canonical.

The server is run by a team of five mods who you can learn more about via the mods page. We cultivate an easygoing and open atmosphere, with member comfort and happiness being our top priority.

All of the links are in the drop down menu under Rowlet, labeled Pokémon! Hovering over each Pokémon will tell you what page they link to!

summary: Like you can feel like a total apex predator then you see something that thinks you're so small you aren't even worth the...
caption:
Like you can feel like a total apex predator then you see something that thinks you’re so small you aren’t even worth the decency of death and suddenly the world feels a lot bigger

———————————————-

Baloo: Ok… We’re getting close to the pool so be ca- -whyhasgodforsakenme- <:U

Critias: -grab- >n<
Baloo: hngk… Thanks Critias. We need torches down here
Critias: Mother of dragons…

Baloo: What? What is… That…
Critias: The pale hide… Pink markings… Its massive
Baloo: That couldn’t be… They don’t get that big! Nothing is supposed t get that big!

Baloo: This is very very not good… Look at the size of that thing! Its easily a titan class if not leviathan… We need to go! Hapu needs to know there is a giant world serpent living in this cavern
